The paper deals with Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR) and its impact on Alzheimer's disease (AD) detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and speech recognition. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with healthcare-related research, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
